Pylighter is an internal, open-source tool that allows us to connect a city and a brand to any transaction, where possible. Here is how the data team uses it to:

  • monitor and measure our algorithms;
  • improve our cashback engine;
  • improve our market knowledge for presale analysis or campaign reports.
